pageContext.claim: “Republicans on the Homeland Security Committee are wasting their time. Democrats, despite all of the evidence, proof and Caravans coming, are not going to give money to build the DESPERATELY needed WALL. I've got you covered. Wall is already being built, I don't expect much help!”
pageContext.analysis: No segment of Trump's promised wall has been built. It's unclear why Trump would agree to reopen the government if he didn't think Democrats on this committee would consider funding his wall or some other acceptable alternative.
